{"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Other Formatting Options","modules":[{"name":"DocC"}]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/docc\/other-formatting-options"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"DocC offers support for various types of elements such as "},{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tables"}],"type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"tables","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.docc\/documentation\/docc\/adding-tables-of-data"},{"text":", notes, and asides.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Add-Notes-and-Other-Asides","type":"heading","text":"Add Notes and Other Asides","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There may be circumstances when you want to get the reader’s attention to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"provide additional advice, or to warn them about common errors or requisite"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"configuration. For those situations, use an aside.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"DocC supports the following types of asides:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Type"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"General information that applies to some users.","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Important"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Important information, such as a requirement."}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Warning"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Critical information, like potential data loss or an irrecoverable state.","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tip"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helpful information, such as shortcuts, suggestions, or hints.","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Experiment"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Instructional information to reinforce a learning objective, or to encourage developers to try out different parts of your framework."}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To create an aside, begin a new line with a greater-than symbol (","type":"text"},{"code":">","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), add a space,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the type of the aside, a colon (","type":"text"},{"code":":","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), and the content of the aside.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["> Tip: Sloths require sustenance to perform activities."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"markdown"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For the example above, DocC renders the following aside:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Tip","style":"tip"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The text of an aside can use the same style attributes as other text, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"include links to other content, including symbols. However, asides don’t provide support for multiple paragraphs, lists, code blocks, or images.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Include Special Characters in Text","anchor":"Include-Special-Characters-in-Text","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To escape one or more special characters, precede each with a backslash"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","t